Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先用过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井先生需要的话  就点些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有早餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激筱塚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你没有撕掉那封信的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前夜就见不到由绮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白您说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了我的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就算是回礼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您看过演唱会了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是由绮小姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就是个碍事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时就像这样  一一提醒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强人所难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就告诉您一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七濑君  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父  伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的错…因为我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先关掉煤气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐节？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年二月末召开  由东央电视台举办的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写作明星  读作维纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维纳斯音乐节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启明之星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决出明日之星  年轻女性歌手限定的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常看的  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮要在维纳斯出场？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还并没有决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是报了名  并不一定会被选上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟由绮小姐才只出了一张单曲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果出场的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然就算出场也不等于稳坐明星之座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但影响力一旦向全国蔓延  势必会掀起一股风潮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获奖的话将更不可想像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是检验我们事务所的能力的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最大的障碍是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得理奈…小姐是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次也没有出场过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两次获得出场机会  却都刚好有别的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是她本人的意愿？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚  谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是绪方先生故意操作的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要与平庸之辈为伍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平庸干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比试高下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  那他这次应该也不会同意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把维纳斯的资料给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还赶得上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说…他改变想法了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像他的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像啊  很像绪方先生的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本来就那么让人琢磨不透吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后  突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战利品的收取
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那…之后？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈的话肯定能通过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能一起出场的话  由绮也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个事务所限定只出场一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是个惯例
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却是个不可打破的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我宝贵的由绮…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮她知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不会想到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也没有说过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音乐节的事的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也该想办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这段恋情结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱塚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有您的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请转告说我已经回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱塚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人溜跶着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您二位是家属吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经联系过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却只有电话留言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  居然是电话留言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大过年的还这么忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父为了我们…连料理都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么和冬弥说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再哭丧着脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让我后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先到先得  先到先得哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面的东西绝对够份量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让您吃亏的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  别挤了别挤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:13.10,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛という形無いもの　とらわれている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:20.74,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心臓が止まるような恋が　あること知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:29.01,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}会うたびに与えてくれた　憧れでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.10,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今でも信じて…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:13.10,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不知不觉  深陷爱的囚牢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:20.74,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我早已知道  爱会让心脏停跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:29.01,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但渴望见你的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.10,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}总让我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:40.83,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}お互いの気持ちはいつも　側にいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:40.83,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}两人的心意不会变  就在彼此身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.17,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}…のない情熱は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:52.65,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}どこから来るの？どこかに眠っているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.99,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ララ　星が…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.17,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不知不觉  深陷爱的囚牢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:20.74,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我早已知道  爱会让心脏停跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:29.01,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但渴望见你的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.10,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}总让我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论有几张也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一幅画召集起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涨潮的时候到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙照顾了  弗兰奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  这副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我屈服了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬弥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井外出中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在信号后…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我是七濑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我打过来好几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我现在在市立医院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上  伯父病情突然恶化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到消息后请赶快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有我们在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥生小姐  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  赶快出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是血压稍微有点高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  刚好正月难得回家  美咲你们也在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸太兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是没什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有些检查什么的  就是手术可能要延后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎非常沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是无颜面对藤井君  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这样的  这也是没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前夜时在这里见过的由绮的经纪人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去过echoes一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君不在的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她偶尔会来坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是那里气氛很轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有别的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长说她经常接送你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计不知道吧  没有谈起过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前还以为是个可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光对由绮  对藤井君也很照顾呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之老爸似乎不用担心了  我要回去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美咲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再待一会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是这样  今天照X光时发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要不要切说是要看今后检查的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起搏器？所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探病嘛  突然大家一起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸…你看  他会察觉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大伯你也很忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泽仓小姐  请不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我这知老又不服老的性格不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你  还捡回一条命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手术延期了让我松了口气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说还要给我安“肉搏器”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是想想心脏好像就要停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉搏？伯父…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你们两人在我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和七濑君好好相处…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥就请你忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:13:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得很奇怪  这样球不就掉到海里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不掉下去  绝对要打回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没打到掉下去怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就追加一百球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  那就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等变得更暖和点了  再过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我网球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在冬弥的房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才说A型的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  竖起耳朵听好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是要去的朋友家碰巧在那附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在简历上看到过  就觉得很近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友不在家…当然是女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和男朋友出去了  又是圣诞前夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就顺路去看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好樵夫回来了  但我可没在等他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过站在门外说话也不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得送他录音电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不设置好的话又有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井现在外出中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在信号音之后留下事情和名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我是由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…有点不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬弥君回家去了吗  还是在医院？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父身体怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能去探望真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正月也结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:16:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然由绮因为一直在工作没什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上的话我在家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果方便的话请打个电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…嗯  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在进入正题之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的路上没有被跟踪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥生小姐  我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维纳斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  墨水省下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老糊涂了吗  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明到今天为止连提都不提一个字的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想出场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想  一直都想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎么办  应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原则是一家事务所只能派一人出场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者一个组合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于两人平分秋色的我社来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人烦恼的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…可…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话答案不是已经出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点犹豫都不用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  那是为了由绮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我遵从决定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  正相反吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起  绪方理奈从绪方事务所独立
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这次又能为我省下些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱片的出版费
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后的工作  拜托送我回公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没打算去音乐节什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪方先生  你不阻止她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥生小姐  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么能这么平静  理奈都要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说要不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送我  带我去理奈那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在下面等我  我去把车子开过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标是那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您竟然察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是平良木君吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍下你们的照片  他想干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装作不知道  或是准备付诸法律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:20:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对由绮不利的话  我可绝不原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈小姐应该也帮了一次忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要被击垮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绪方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小英  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是神崎社长  竟然能追我到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿能见个面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长  玛瑙小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我是由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由绮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.67,0:24:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十七页
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.38,0:24:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望被揭穿的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.61,0:24:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和希望不被相信的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.34,0:24:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.69,0:24:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,White  Album

